ax_client = AxClient()
ax_client.create_experiment(parameters=[{'name': 'x', 'type': 'range',
    'bounds': [-5.0, 10.0]}, {'name': 'y', 'type': 'range', 'bounds': [0.0,
    1.0]}], minimize=True)
for _ in range(6):
    parameterization, trial_index = ax_client.get_next_trial()
    x, y = parameterization.get('x'), parameterization.get('y')
    ax_client.complete_trial(trial_index, raw_data=[({'y': y / 2.0}, {
        'objective': (branin(x, y / 2.0), 0.0)}), ({'y': y}, {'objective':
        (branin(x, y), 0.0)})])
